600 Thousand People Did Not Manage to Renew Driver's Licenses
Six hundred thousand drivers missed the deadline and failed to renew their old drivers' licenses, which will end in the year.
Today is the last day for people to apply for the renewal so that the authorities can secure the new license by the end of the year.
